response.overview: NST Bike New Zealand brings the world’s best freeride mountain bikers to Queenstown’s stunning Mt. Dewar. This groundbreaking event blends big mountain terrain with freestyle features across intersecting lines, redefining traditional formats.  Elite riders from big mountain, slopestyle, freeride and downhill showcase the pinnacle of the sport in this thrilling rider-driven competition.
